Moral pressure & civic mobilization

Drive bottom-up demand, complement top-down diplomacy

This layered and inclusive adoption path integrates both
governmental institutions and global civil society, offering
practical incentives while aligning with constitutional
legitimacy and the no-single-leader ethos embedded in the
ethics round table and enforcement institutions.

